            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="span3">
            <div class="well well-small">
                <h5>Scholarship</h5>
                <br />
                <h6>Donate to the Scholarship Fund!</h6>
                <img id="previewImage" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif" border="0" alt="Preview Image">
